messages.title: THE GENERAL ELECTION IS A TWO HORSE RACE
messages.content: It’s a straight fight between Labour and the Tories. Don’t risk staying at home and not voting on Thursday May 6th 2010 or the Tories will win.

mentions.tacticalSituation: It’s a straight fight between Labour and the Tories.

issues.economy: The choice is about the sort of future you want for Daventry. Britain is on the road to recovery. Don't let the Tories wreck it.

images.caption: THE GENERAL ELECTION IS A TWO HORSE RACE

leaflet.additionalNotes: IT'S YOUR FUTURE. VOTE FOR IT.
